categories: Category:Cut content from Rogue One: A Star Wars Story

nodes.text: Jerris Kestal was an individual who served the Rebel Alliance as a member of Rogue One alongside K-2SO, Jyn Erso, Senna, Lunak, Ria Talla and Dray Nevis.
Jerris Kestal was one of several characters conceived to be a part of the Rogue One team seen in the film Rogue One: A Star Wars Story, but was cut from the final film.
